title.en: Isekai no Boukun Outaishi ni Metorare Soudesu!? ~Tensei Majo wa Kuroki Ookami ni Kyuuaisareru~

description.en:
"Rejoice. I shall make you my wife."

When Yuki, a company slave who is about to lose her life in an accident, wakes up, she's suddenly in a fantasy world! I thought that I could live a life of reincarnation in a different world, but I ended up being chased by Gorotsuki, and the place where I escaped was a brothel. Then I was treated as a witch and ended up in even more danger!

Under these circumstances, thanks to the mysterious knight Matthias, I survived the situation for a while, but the cost of being helped was my body. Forcible kissing and sweet caress... Matthias likes Yuki who behaves patiently even though she seems to be swept away by the pleasures she is given.

Wait a minute! He's the first prince of this country!? And I was enthusiastically proposed to "make sure I belong to him"!?

[b]Chinese[/b]
包子脸社畜OL在意外事故中转生到了异世界
